1
00:00:10,300 --> 00:00:11,181
Lord,

2
00:00:11,741 --> 00:00:13,581
we come before you

3
00:00:13,860 --> 00:00:15,061
to witness

4
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:16,140
and bless this man and woman

5
00:00:16,180 --> 00:00:19,061
as they enter the sacred covenant of marriage.

6
00:00:19,620 --> 00:00:20,941
Amen.

7
00:00:21,500 --> 00:00:22,300
Bride,

8
00:00:22,741 --> 00:00:24,941
do you take this man

9
00:00:24,941 --> 00:00:26,180
to be your husband,

10
00:00:26,581 --> 00:00:28,581
to covenant with him in marriage?

11
00:00:29,660 --> 00:00:30,661
I do.

12
00:00:31,260 --> 00:00:32,061
Groom,

13
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:33,820
will you take this woman

14
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:35,900
as your wife?

15
00:00:38,460 --> 00:00:40,101
He doesn't seem willing.

16
00:00:43,301 --> 00:00:45,140
Though I'm abroad,

17
00:00:45,381 --> 00:00:48,621
I know what's going on at home.

18
00:00:51,820 --> 00:00:52,940
Your marriage

19
00:00:52,940 --> 00:00:55,180
ties two families.

20
00:00:55,701 --> 00:00:58,180
I hope you'll take it seriously.

21
00:00:58,940 --> 00:00:59,860
Chengyan,

22
00:01:00,021 --> 00:01:01,260
the one you want to marry

23
00:01:01,500 --> 00:01:02,901
isn't Xia Wanqing, is it?

24
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:08,020
So, are you going to

25
00:01:08,020 --> 00:01:09,901
get married or not?

26
00:01:10,421 --> 00:01:11,421
It's up to you.

27
00:01:20,140 --> 00:01:21,020
Are you?

28
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:27,621
Young Master Yan,

29
00:01:28,061 --> 00:01:29,380
just marry Miss Xia.

30
00:01:37,621 --> 00:01:38,981
Who do you think you are?

31
00:01:39,860 --> 00:01:41,621
How come you have to decide

32
00:01:42,220 --> 00:01:43,660
whether he gets married or not?

33
00:01:44,860 --> 00:01:45,781
I...

34
00:01:47,461 --> 00:01:48,181
Xia Wanqing,

35
00:01:48,461 --> 00:01:49,300
you've gone too far.

36
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:50,421
How could you hit someone?

37
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:51,300
What are you doing?

38
00:01:53,261 --> 00:01:54,541
Looks like

39
00:01:54,821 --> 00:01:57,020
the one you want to marry is her, huh?

40
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:00,901
Once you step through this gate,

41
00:02:00,981 --> 00:02:02,421
every place you see

42
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:03,580
belongs to the Gu family.

43
00:02:03,740 --> 00:02:05,781
The Gu family's layout is very particular.

44
00:02:06,181 --> 00:02:08,500
The building opposite is the residence of Young Master Jing.

45
00:02:08,500 --> 00:02:10,141
This side is the residence of Young Master Yan.

46
00:02:10,461 --> 00:02:11,940
Old Master Gu has just passed away not long ago.

47
00:02:11,980 --> 00:02:14,260
This topic must never be mentioned in the Gu family.

48
00:02:14,461 --> 00:02:16,741
Mrs. Gu and the Second Master are temporarily abroad.

49
00:02:16,861 --> 00:02:18,141
The Gu family has only two young masters.

50
00:02:18,380 --> 00:02:20,141
Everything must be done according to their instructions.

51
00:02:20,420 --> 00:02:21,781
The Gu family has many rules.

52
00:02:21,901 --> 00:02:23,781
Although you are the personal care for Young Master Yan,

53
00:02:23,820 --> 00:02:25,700
you must also wear the uniform of the Gu family.

54
00:02:25,940 --> 00:02:26,901
Change it later.

55
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:31,581
Young Master Yan, your new nurse has arrived.

56
00:02:31,861 --> 00:02:32,700
Come in.

57
00:02:39,820 --> 00:02:41,581
I have a nursing job here.

58
00:02:41,940 --> 00:02:43,181
I don't know if you're interested.

59
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:44,301
It's my brother.

60
00:02:44,781 --> 00:02:46,061
He had a car accident six months ago.

61
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:47,660
His legs are still recovering.

62
00:02:48,021 --> 00:02:49,220
He needs someone to take care of him.

63
00:02:49,621 --> 00:02:51,380
No problem, I can do it.

64
00:02:52,141 --> 00:02:54,820
But his emotions are not very stable.

65
00:02:55,700 --> 00:02:56,621
He gets angry easily.

66
00:02:56,901 --> 00:02:57,741
Young Master Yan.

67
00:03:00,061 --> 00:03:00,861
Young Master Yan.

68
00:03:11,781 --> 00:03:12,540
Young Master Yan.

69
00:03:12,901 --> 00:03:14,621
I... I'm Ji Xiaoxue,

70
00:03:14,861 --> 00:03:16,621
your new personal caregiver.

71
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:32,500
Young Master Yan, what are you doing?

72
00:03:38,901 --> 00:03:40,100
I need a bath.

73
00:03:42,980 --> 00:03:43,940
Go fill the tub.

74
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:47,260
Okay.

75
00:03:51,420 --> 00:03:54,181
Young Master Yan, the water's ready.

76
00:03:58,061 --> 00:03:59,420
Come, put your hand on me.

77
00:04:13,660 --> 00:04:14,860
You must be the personal nurse

78
00:04:14,860 --> 00:04:16,420
that Jing hired to take care of Chengyan.

79
00:04:17,261 --> 00:04:19,261
Your name is Ji...

80
00:04:19,781 --> 00:04:20,821
Ji Xiaoxue.

81
00:04:22,420 --> 00:04:24,860
I'm his fiancée, Xia Wanqing.

82
00:04:25,781 --> 00:04:26,781
Nice to meet you, Miss Xia.

83
00:04:27,740 --> 00:04:28,740
I'm free today.

84
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:29,540
Let me do it.

85
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:49,540
Who let you in?

86
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:51,740
Young Master Yan.

87
00:04:52,021 --> 00:04:53,180
Who let you in?

88
00:04:54,060 --> 00:04:55,740
I... I just came to clean for you.

89
00:04:55,740 --> 00:04:56,941
Don't you know that without my permission,

90
00:04:56,941 --> 00:04:58,501
no one is allowed in my room?

91
00:04:59,660 --> 00:05:00,781
No one told me.

92
00:05:00,781 --> 00:05:01,701
I'm telling you now,

93
00:05:02,341 --> 00:05:04,141
don't enter my room or touch my things

94
00:05:04,141 --> 00:05:04,941
without my permission,

95
00:05:05,660 --> 00:05:06,501
understood?

96
00:05:10,701 --> 00:05:11,300
Understood.

97
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:12,381
Then get out now!

98
00:05:20,941 --> 00:05:22,740
Young Master Yan, have some water.

99
00:05:26,821 --> 00:05:28,420
And take your medicine.

100
00:05:29,100 --> 00:05:29,701
Get it away.

101
00:05:30,100 --> 00:05:31,941
Miss Xia specifically told me

102
00:05:31,941 --> 00:05:33,300
to make sure you take it on time.

103
00:05:34,180 --> 00:05:35,420
I'm not sick. Why do I need medicine?

104
00:05:50,821 --> 00:05:51,740
Ji Xiaoxue.

105
00:05:52,581 --> 00:05:53,540
Ji Xiaoxue.

106
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:56,660
Young Master Yan, you're looking for me?

107
00:05:56,660 --> 00:05:58,341
I just went to get you breakfast.

108
00:05:58,660 --> 00:05:59,860
You don't have a cane,

109
00:05:59,860 --> 00:06:01,660
so I got you a pair.

110
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:03,300
Now you can get around on your own.

111
00:06:05,220 --> 00:06:06,740
I'll go get breakfast.

112
00:06:10,581 --> 00:06:11,501
You did this on purpose, didn't you?

113
00:06:12,581 --> 00:06:14,620
Don't you know we can't have crutches at home?

114
00:06:15,420 --> 00:06:16,461
If you can't handle it,

115
00:06:16,501 --> 00:06:17,501
you can just leave!

116
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:19,781
I don't need your help!

117
00:06:20,341 --> 00:06:21,381
Take your crutches

118
00:06:21,781 --> 00:06:22,660
and get out!

119
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:50,021
Young Master Yan,

120
00:07:22,381 --> 00:07:23,701
what happened to you?

121
00:07:24,060 --> 00:07:25,341
Accidentally bumped into something.

122
00:07:26,781 --> 00:07:27,901
It was my brother, right?

123
00:07:32,300 --> 00:07:34,261
Then let me apologize on behalf of him.

124
00:07:35,501 --> 00:07:37,100
It's okay, Young Master Jing.

125
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:40,701
Alright.

126
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:43,980
My brother hasn't taken his medicine these days, has he?

127
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:44,980
Yes.

128
00:07:45,220 --> 00:07:47,420
Young Master Yan hasn't been willing to take his medicine lately.

129
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:49,781
He knocked over all his medicine.

130
00:07:49,941 --> 00:07:51,781
I even bought him a cane,

131
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:53,261
but he seems...

132
00:07:53,461 --> 00:07:54,381
It's my fault.

133
00:07:55,060 --> 00:07:56,781
I should have explained.

134
00:07:57,341 --> 00:07:58,901
Ever since my brother's accident,

135
00:07:58,980 --> 00:08:01,100
he gets very agitated around canes.

136
00:08:02,261 --> 00:08:02,821
Here,

137
00:08:04,060 --> 00:08:05,300
this is his new medicine.

138
00:08:05,901 --> 00:08:07,300
Just one pill at a time.

139
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:09,141
He should be more cooperative now.

140
00:08:18,261 --> 00:08:22,381
Why did I take such a demanding patient?

141
00:08:22,901 --> 00:08:24,660
Oh my God.

142
00:08:29,300 --> 00:08:30,101
For money.

143
00:08:30,820 --> 00:08:31,501
Come on.

144
00:08:42,700 --> 00:08:44,340
You're just a dog wagging its tail

145
00:08:44,820 --> 00:08:47,300
in front of him.

146
00:08:52,021 --> 00:08:52,820
Young Master Yan.

147
00:08:52,820 --> 00:08:54,540
You don't want to go to the rehab room, right?

148
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,501
I'll bring all the fitness equipment here.

149
00:09:13,300 --> 00:09:14,420
You don't make mistakes.

150
00:09:14,660 --> 00:09:15,981
I'll make you make mistakes.

151
00:09:30,300 --> 00:09:30,981
Oh no.

152
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:31,981
It's shattered.

153
00:09:34,981 --> 00:09:35,700
My phone.

154
00:09:36,060 --> 00:09:36,741
Thank you.

155
00:09:38,060 --> 00:09:39,820
This is the best gift I've ever received,

156
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:41,540
aside from the one my mom gave me.

157
00:09:55,261 --> 00:09:56,021
Try it.

158
00:09:56,901 --> 00:09:57,741
I don't know how.

159
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:58,861
Give it a try.

160
00:10:06,741 --> 00:10:07,981
I really don't know.

161
00:10:10,381 --> 00:10:11,180
Come on, let me teach you.

162
00:10:11,981 --> 00:10:12,660
Okay.

163
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:19,101
Sit on my lap.

164
00:10:21,180 --> 00:10:23,101
How can I teach you if you don't sit on my lap?

165
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:25,021
My legs are numb.

166
00:10:37,621 --> 00:10:38,540
Relax your fingers.

167
00:10:39,060 --> 00:10:39,861
Don't use too much force.

168
00:10:40,021 --> 00:10:41,340
Don't lean forward,

169
00:10:41,781 --> 00:10:42,820
nor lean back.

170
00:10:43,420 --> 00:10:44,901
Don't hold the string for too long,

171
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:46,621
or it will be easy to lose accuracy.

172
00:10:47,901 --> 00:10:49,021
Keep your eyes on the target.

173
00:10:58,141 --> 00:10:59,101
You nailed it!

174
00:11:11,580 --> 00:11:12,901
I've got a gift for you.

175
00:11:16,621 --> 00:11:18,221
What a pretty brooch!

176
00:11:19,540 --> 00:11:21,381
This is the best gift

177
00:11:21,660 --> 00:11:23,101
I've ever received, aside from my mom's.

178
00:12:18,300 --> 00:12:20,060
Young Master Yan, what would you like to drink?

179
00:12:24,101 --> 00:12:26,261
Isn't it too early for alcohol?

180
00:12:30,381 --> 00:12:31,021
It's fine.

181
00:12:34,861 --> 00:12:36,060
Then, eat up first.

182
00:12:43,381 --> 00:12:44,340
I'd like a sandwich.

183
00:12:44,901 --> 00:12:46,141
Okay, I'll go make it right away.

184
00:12:49,940 --> 00:12:52,021
Qingyou, would you like some coffee?

185
00:12:52,981 --> 00:12:53,621
Sure.

186
00:12:54,021 --> 00:12:54,621
Where's my brother?

187
00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:00,261
I'll go make a cup for you.

188
00:13:11,221 --> 00:13:12,700
Has he been taking his medicine on time?

189
00:13:12,901 --> 00:13:13,901
Has he been getting angry?

190
00:13:14,381 --> 00:13:15,101
No.

191
00:13:15,221 --> 00:13:16,820
I secretly put the medicine in his wine.

192
00:13:20,621 --> 00:13:21,820
That way, he won't know.

193
00:13:31,460 --> 00:13:32,180
Let me help you.

194
00:13:58,381 --> 00:14:00,060
Young Master Jing, I'm sorry.

195
00:14:00,060 --> 00:14:01,501
I didn't mean to.

196
00:14:01,861 --> 00:14:03,501
If you can't reach it, just tell me.

197
00:14:04,741 --> 00:14:06,221
You're the master.

198
00:14:06,221 --> 00:14:07,700
How could I...

199
00:14:09,060 --> 00:14:11,021
From now on, if you need anything,

200
00:14:11,381 --> 00:14:12,261
just come to me.

201
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:20,180
Qingyou,

202
00:14:21,141 --> 00:14:22,381
this is the coffee for you.

203
00:14:23,621 --> 00:14:24,781
What are you...

204
00:14:26,180 --> 00:14:27,261
What are you doing?

205
00:14:28,381 --> 00:14:30,381
There was a little accident just now.

206
00:14:31,420 --> 00:14:33,420
I'll clean up and go to the company.

207
00:14:34,501 --> 00:14:35,580
Brother, it's so delicious.

208
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:40,940
Mr. Gu Chengyan,

209
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:43,420
the acquisition plan of Su's Art Gallery

210
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:45,660
has been mentioned by the media recently.

211
00:14:46,101 --> 00:14:47,300
We should pay more attention to it.

212
00:14:47,540 --> 00:14:49,660
I hope all the subsequent problems can be solved.

213
00:14:50,621 --> 00:14:51,981
That's all for today's meeting.

214
00:14:52,221 --> 00:14:53,101
Dismissed.

215
00:15:01,420 --> 00:15:02,781
Do you have any questions, Jing?

216
00:15:04,381 --> 00:15:06,901
I don't quite understand...

217
00:15:12,700 --> 00:15:13,700
That's good enough.

218
00:15:14,340 --> 00:15:16,340
Jing, I didn't drive today.

219
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:19,060
Could you give me a ride home after work?

220
00:15:19,300 --> 00:15:19,940
Sure.

221
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:30,221
Let's go.

222
00:15:37,940 --> 00:15:39,060
Qing, your lipstick.

223
00:15:45,180 --> 00:15:46,861
It's Wanqing.

224
00:16:30,981 --> 00:16:31,621
Uncle.

225
00:16:32,261 --> 00:16:32,861
Chengyan,

226
00:16:33,300 --> 00:16:35,381
how's your leg?

227
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:37,261
It's recovering.

228
00:16:37,381 --> 00:16:38,540
Good.
